10    /**
11    * Helper container used for resolving serializers for dynamic (possibly but not
12    * necessarily polymorphic) properties: properties whose type is not forced
13    * to use dynamic (declared) type and that are not final.
14    * If so, serializer to use can only be established once actual value type is known.
15    * Since this happens a lot unless static typing is forced (or types are final)
16    * this implementation is optimized for efficiency.
17    * Instances are immutable; new instances are created with factory methods: this
18    * is important to ensure correct multi-threaded access.
19    */
